summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of MUJ Campus Marketplace. Major improvements from previous test - session management fixed, wishlist buttons working. Core marketplace functionality working well (85% success rate). Navigation issues remain with protected routes and Sell button.

ui_bugs.issue: Sell button in navbar does not navigate to Add Product page when clicked

integration_issues.issue: Direct URL access to /add-product and /my-listings redirects to login page even when user is authenticated

passed_tests: Landing page loads with correct branding and content
User login with demo@muj.manipal.edu / demo123 works
User authentication persists (Sell button appears when logged in)
Category filters work perfectly (All, Room Essentials, Books & Study, Electronics, Other Stuff)
Product cards display with images, titles, prices, categories
Wishlist heart buttons present and clickable on all product cards
Product detail page navigation works (clicking product cards)
Profile page accessible and shows user information
Marketplace displays products correctly (5 items found)
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix Sell button navigation to Add Product page. Fix protected route authentication guard - users should be able to access /add-product and /my-listings when authenticated. These are the only remaining navigation issues preventing 100% functionality.
